{"tid":158593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歌手關淑怡涉刑恐被捕","createTime":"2017-03-16T11:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T03:40:54.000Z","uid":47272,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59f5f42724fc54710930aa3a60ac085252af1e90","tid":158593,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"歌手關淑怡涉刑恐被捕！據悉，事發於今日清晨5時許，警方接報一名年約50歲姓關女子，在大嶼山愉景灣一間酒店的餐廳大吵大鬧，其間有人受傷。據現場消息稱，肇事的姓關女子為歌手關淑怡(英文名Shirley)，當時她在餐廳內要求職員落單，其間雙方發生爭執，關一度發難並疑出手襲擊職員，及曾出言恐嚇對方。<br />\n<br />\n其後警方接報到場，將涉嫌刑事恐嚇及普通襲擊的姓關女子拘捕，交由大嶼山警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。目前受傷的職員清醒送往北大嶼山醫院治理。而疑犯已獲保釋候查，3月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170316&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56437644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170316%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56437644&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=05395945\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170316%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56437644&h=206f6f65\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170316&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56437644</a>"},{"pid":"1e62250e704c8f633c07f2166b77641d5d944e8a","tid":158593,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd3c74c75c77c04594e2d2f87bedb9df25709f2f","tid":158593,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:31:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebe4a045e44992b6fea2d0a157eaca291fd756a7","tid":158593,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"上次自殺，今次打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b0462c89fd539e294b74039b2cc8b9e7f76ec6","tid":158593,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ca1d574d64ff716e8c548f9cdfc298019c75862b","tid":158593,"uid":39800,"like":0,